{"tid":2411511,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我與Lympho （癌魔）有個約會.... (2) 治療","createTime":"2021-02-17T11:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T21:05:10.000Z","uid":391992,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"73b600d4438e88598762dccd34da3f11a5cc37f4","tid":2411511,"uid":391992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"上集重溫:<br />\n我與Lympho 有個約會.... (1) 確診<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2409064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2409064</a><br />\n<br />\n[純粹分享個人經驗及心得，希望幫到正在抗癌嘅你或者照顧者]<br />\n因為正身處醫院staycation ，回覆較慢請見諒<br />\n<br />\n上次講左確診會做嘅程序，今次講下治療過程<br />\n<br />\n其實淋巴癌主要做化療去醫<br />\n咩係化療呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以毒攻毒！ 殺曬所有癌細胞，<br />\n但同時係會破壞你其他正常嘅細胞<br />\n所以經常見到好多副作用(下次再講)<br />\n<br />\n化療點做呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似吊鹽水咁。 滴滴滴<br />\n最常見就係去日間中心，<br />\n大概要大半日時間坐定定等藥入晒你個身到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n*記得要有人陪住走，一旦打完化療藥，身體好虛弱，易暈無力會氣喘<br />\n<br />\n咁都有例外嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就係活生生例子<br />\n因為我同時間驗出有兩種不同嘅癌細胞<br />\n醫生建議我要接受24hrs x 4days 嘅化療馬拉松<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次住一星期醫院<br />\n*最近relapse <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n住院期間我要做啲咩呢？<br />\n1. 驗血，驗尿 （睇下你肝腎功能、血指數等等）<br />\n2. 心臟超聲波 （唔會次次做，睇下個心頂唔頂得住啲藥<br />\n3.照肺 （睇下有無肺炎）<br />\n4. 吸霧化藥 （聞氣，預防肺炎）一個月一次<br />\n<br />\n基本上我一打藥就血壓低，會有少少作嘔感覺<br />\n但我一次都未嘔過<br />\n記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當你開始有少少心口悶好似想嘔，快啲出聲要打止嘔藥，你等嘔先用藥已經遲，口服藥仲有機會嘔翻出黎<br />\n因為藥物入到體內要最少半個鐘吸收，嘔先出聲要藥，頭尾都辛苦自己一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n血壓低會令你容易暈低<br />\n我試過去廁所著翻條褲，因為動作太快，頭又dup低<br />\n眼前一閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />𠼱低左，要五個人夾翻我上床<br />\n最驚係你一個唔小心跌穿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n通常做完化療都會隔二星期再做嘅<br />\n7日後，係你白血球最低嘅時候<br />\n免疫力最差，唔好出街！！！<br />\n唔好比自己有機會受感染<br />\n(遲啲再講注意事項)<br />\n所以會有升白血球針比你翻屋企每日自己啪一針<br />\n仲要覆診，驗血，起碼覆3次<br />\n<br />\n以上過程會重複到醫生認為你無癌細胞就會停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次就講下 副作用 同埋 做化療期間日常起居注意啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都好多細微野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好好照顧自己同身邊病人啦"},{"pid":"6c4bb845792411f15b58792ff60a3814208997c7","tid":2411511,"uid":197074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"睇到要做咁多野都心痛你"},{"pid":"fc4614bece362b49707b7855f248672136c765c7","tid":2411511,"uid":214491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"我都係癌症康復者，祝樓主早日戰勝病魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5761170f676639d0afd2e5c9a87a1611f89350b","tid":2411511,"uid":118490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:06:49.000Z","msg":"多謝你無私分享<br />\n祝早日康復"},{"pid":"5ff127d0abf34f6821b06c950e05d76b56c9e2f9","tid":2411511,"uid":61934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:54:06.000Z","msg":"祝早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2年前我都有DLBCL，同你一樣又係Chemo 馬拉松，而家 Touchwood 穩定左，定期覆診都無異樣，所以絕對明白你當中辛酸，加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae71eec5b89b2f949abaa4e619b3ca8dae342ea4","tid":2411511,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"祝早日康復，身體健康"},{"pid":"94d64b483832e1831e86279fb18194018ceea3d3","tid":2411511,"uid":9452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"祝你早日康復！"},{"pid":"368dabcac5d655102e7fae22b1eabf39346bb747","tid":2411511,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"how old  睇你描寫個人好&lsquo;規&lsquo; 下🤔 ❓"},{"pid":"a7b244ca501afd7a0386341967a2e1376afd6c42","tid":2411511,"uid":391992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"368dabcac5d655102e7fae22b1eabf39346bb747","tid":2411511,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"how old  睇你描寫個人好&lsquo;規&lsquo; 下🤔 ❓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n虧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲係副作用，毒藥有邊個受得到<br />\n你試過啦？ 分享下你嘅體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲人每次去一日day center化療已經頂唔順，<br />\n我算係咁，體重無暴跌"},{"pid":"77da07612ef36ce6b562e3e302529ea471e60f67","tid":2411511,"uid":391992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ff127d0abf34f6821b06c950e05d76b56c9e2f9","tid":2411511,"uid":61934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:54:06.000Z","msg":"祝早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2年前我都有DLBCL，同你一樣又係Chemo 馬拉松，而家 Touchwood 穩定左，定期覆診都無異樣，所以絕對明白你當中辛酸，加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:12:32.000Z","msg":"多謝 <br />\n你守多3年就掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf206d00ab5e5df2e795240630c3380441c2675","tid":2411511,"uid":391992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc4614bece362b49707b7855f248672136c765c7","tid":2411511,"uid":214491,"like":0,"dislike":0