cking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />越礦飛車急轉彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗翻起覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c95ce3f179956cdcd0f30516c174078c490010","tid":2411511,"uid":63479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2259214e85311b93262ce46e5a01f51c12dd4645","tid":2411511,"uid":391992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1cd654d2a9eb4352f94d7ea0d1b56badd776db6","tid":2411511,"uid":63479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73b600d4438e88598762dccd34da3f11a5cc37f4","tid":2411511,"uid":391992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"上集重溫:<br />\n我與Lympho 有個約會.... (1) 確診<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2409064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2409064</a><br />\n<br />\n[純粹分享個人經驗及心得，希望幫到正在抗癌嘅你或者照顧者]<br />\n因為正身處醫院staycation ，回覆較慢請見諒<br />\n<br />\n上次講左確診會做嘅程序，今次講下治療過程<br />\n<br />\n其實淋巴癌主要做化療去醫<br />\n咩係化療呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以毒攻毒！ 殺曬所有癌細胞，<br />\n但同時係會破壞你其他正常嘅細胞<br />\n所以經常見到好多副作用(下次再講)<br />\n<br />\n化療點做呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似吊鹽水咁。 滴滴滴<br />\n最常見就係去日間中心，<br />\n大概要大半日時間坐定定等藥入晒你個身到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n*記得要有人陪住走，一旦打完化療藥，身體好虛弱，易暈無力會氣喘<br />\n<br />\n咁都有例外嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就係活生生例子<br />\n因為我同時間驗出有兩種不同嘅癌細胞<br />\n醫生建議我要接受24hrs x 4days 嘅化療馬拉松<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次住一星期醫院<br />\n*最近relapse <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n住院期間我要做啲咩呢？<br />\n1. 驗血，驗尿 （睇下你肝腎功能、血指數等等）<br />\n2. 心臟超聲波 （唔會次次做，睇下個心頂唔頂得住啲藥<br />\n3.照肺 （睇下有無肺炎）<br />\n4. 吸霧化藥 （聞氣，預防肺炎）一個月一次<br />\n<br />\n基本上我一打藥就血壓低，會有少少作嘔感覺<br />\n但我一次都未嘔過<br />\n記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當你開始有少少心口悶好似想嘔，快啲出聲要打止嘔藥，你等嘔先用藥已經遲，口服藥仲有機會嘔翻出黎<br />\n因為藥物入到體內要最少半個鐘吸收，嘔先出聲要藥，頭尾都辛苦自己一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n血壓低會令你容易暈低<br />\n我試過去廁所著翻條褲，因為動作太快，頭又dup低<br />\n眼前一閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />𠼱低左，要五個人夾翻我上床<br />\n最驚係你一個唔小心跌穿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n通常做完化療都會隔二星期再做嘅<br />\n7日後，係你白血球最低嘅時候<br />\n免疫力最差，唔好出街！！！<br />\n唔好比自己有機會受感染<br />\n(遲啲再講注意事項)<br />\n所以會有升白血球針比你翻屋企每日自己啪一針<br />\n仲要覆診，驗血，起碼覆3次<br />\n<br />\n以上過程會重複到醫生認為你無癌細胞就會停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次就講下 副作用 同埋 做化療期間日常起居注意啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都好多細微野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好好照顧自己同身邊病人啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:39:05.000Z","msg":"巴打好勁<br />\n我覺得自己bone marrow都挨唔住<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"我琴日出左院啦，好多謝各位集氣為我加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說今次再入院 bone marrow 拮左我左右兩邊<br />\n我忍唔住係個過程亂噏廿四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當枝針轉到入臀骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我同醫生護士講，<br />\n不得了吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />越礦飛車急轉彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗翻起覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:23:57.000Z","msg":"其實局部麻醉係咪冇乜用？<br />\n成日見病人係轉入去果下好痛<br />\n問返佢哋係怨怨痛"},{"pid":"1eaf3646b575a38be83215b14f55c3c3bfffe6f3","tid":2411511,"uid":391992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11c95ce3f179956cdcd0f30516c174078c490010","tid":2411511,"uid":63479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2259214e85311b93262ce46e5a01f51c12dd4645","tid":2411511,"uid":391992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1cd654d2a9eb4352f94d7ea0d1b56badd776db6","tid":2411511,"uid":63479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:39:05.000Z","msg":"巴打好勁<br />\n我覺得自己bone marrow都挨唔住<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"我琴日出左院啦，好多謝各位集氣為我加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說今次再入院 bone marrow 拮左我左右兩邊<br />\n我忍唔住係個過程亂噏廿四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當枝針轉到入臀骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我同醫生護士講，<br />\n不得了吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />越礦飛車急轉彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗翻起覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"